data.title: William Preston of Newcastle-upon-Tyne, England and...
data.meta_description: William Preston, son of Henry Preston and Jane Lawson, was baptized 30 April 1650 in Newcastle-upon-Tyne, Northumberland, England. He married Ann Taylor, daughter of Edward Taylor and Margaret, 10 September 1672 in North Shields, Northumberland. They emigrated in 1683 and settled in Pennsylvania. He died in 1717.
